description.en: Mewtwo Inu - An Anime Token Launchpad built on Ethereum bridging the world of Anime with Cryptocurrency. MewPad will be the launchpad platform where Anime Project Owners can launch their tokens safely. Much like many other launchpads, project owners will be able to create Presales, Fair Launches, Lock Liquidity/Token even Create a Token. Users can browse the Launchpad and view trending presales. The most advanced Tools System for Cryptocurrency, Mewtwo likes to call it the Google of Anime Charting platforms. Users will be able to change between different Networks to check any and all tokens under each Network. Mewtwo Inu Project aims to connect Anime Lovers into the World of Crypto by introducing Anime Styled designs on our Dapps, making the DeFi experience stylish and cool.
